00:44:52,109 --> 00:44:53,486
Whenever you're ready, Al.

525
00:44:53,694 --> 00:44:55,613
- Come on!
- What are we doing?

526
00:44:56,322 --> 00:44:58,991
- I don't think you should be doing that.
- Okay. Drop it.

527
00:44:59,200 --> 00:45:01,410
- We're good.
- Yeah?

528
00:45:01,619 --> 00:45:03,079
- All right, hold on.
- Hold on.

529
00:45:03,287 --> 00:45:04,747
Okay.

530
00:45:09,543 --> 00:45:10,795
Al!

531
00:45:19,637 --> 00:45:21,055
Hey, I need a life jacket.

532
00:45:40,157 --> 00:45:41,784
Crap.

