00:47:05,201 --> 00:47:06,661
Why?

559
00:47:14,752 --> 00:47:17,963
God! What is the secret
to this thing?

560
00:47:18,214 --> 00:47:20,675
Just wrap it around your nugget.

561
00:47:21,384 --> 00:47:25,137
- What part? Here? This?
- Yeah.

562
00:47:26,430 --> 00:47:29,266
Well, how come yours stays on?

563
00:47:29,892 --> 00:47:31,602
Maybe you got a small head.

564
00:47:31,769 --> 00:47:36,232
I don't think so.
Somebody would've told me.

565
00:48:01,090 --> 00:48:02,717
Thank you.

