00:48:07,888 --> 00:48:09,682
World Health Organization.

567
00:48:10,099 --> 00:48:11,767
Hello?

568
00:48:12,143 --> 00:48:14,061
Is anyone here?

569
00:48:19,900 --> 00:48:21,360
Frank.

570
00:48:21,986 --> 00:48:23,738
Look at this.

571
00:48:38,961 --> 00:48:40,421
Anyone here?

572
00:48:47,011 --> 00:48:48,721
Hello?

573
00:48:53,351 --> 00:48:54,810
Hello?

574
00:49:09,909 --> 00:49:12,036
Oh, my God.

575
00:50:28,362 --> 00:50:31,157
This well was filled in recently.

576
00:50:31,365 --> 00:50:33,826
I think people here knew
the water was making them sick.

577
00:50:34,035 --> 00:50:36,620
I still say we should
let Oumar go down.

578
00:50:36,829 --> 00:50:39,165
Oumar, you wouldn't mind
going down that well, would you?

579
00:50:39,415 --> 00:50:40,875
- No, it's okay. I'll go down.
- You see?

580
00:50:41,125 --> 00:50:42,918
Frank, I'll be fine.

581
00:50:53,304 --> 00:50:55,306
Yeah, there you go.

582
00:50:57,058 --> 00:51:00,144
All right, you're looking good.
You're looking good.

583
00:51:00,728 --> 00:51:02,938
- Give her a little more rope.
- Okay.

584
00:51:06,317 --> 00:51:07,693
Be careful, please.

585
00:51:09,028 --> 00:51:10,529
Just take your time.

586
00:51:11,113 --> 00:51:12,114
Eva.

587
00:51:12,740 --> 00:51:13,991
Eva, hold on.

588
00:51:15,034 --> 00:51:17,495
Eva. Hold on. We've got you.

