00:51:56,659 --> 00:51:58,869
Don't go anywhere.
I'll be right back.

597
00:51:59,078 --> 00:52:00,371
Okay.

598
00:52:00,538 --> 00:52:02,873
Hello there. I'm Dr. Hopper with
