- What are you doing?

600
00:52:06,168 --> 00:52:08,587
Eva, get those... Oh, my God!

601
00:52:09,755 --> 00:52:11,674
- Frank!
- Charlie, please don't shoot me.

602
00:52:12,008 --> 00:52:13,592
Charlie, don't...

603
00:52:40,995 --> 00:52:43,414
Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa,
do you hear that?

604
00:53:06,312 --> 00:53:08,147
- This is all of them?
- Yes, sir.

605
00:53:09,607 --> 00:53:14,528
The UN knows that we're here. This is
a United Nations-sanctioned mission.

